      "examples_for_Rules": [
        "In “Human Nature,” the chorus uses more vocal stacks than the verse, following the rule: intimate verses, expansive choruses.",
        "In “Heat Wave,” stacks are used only on big refrain words (“heat wave!”) so the impact stays sharp instead of muddy."
